flowchart TD
    A[Container becomes dispatch eligible] --> B[RoundManager evaluates state/readiness]
    B --> C{Eligible?}
    C -- No --> R[Reject / diagnostic report]
    C -- Yes --> D[Register container registry index]
    D --> E[TDispatchWaitingList FIFO order]
    E --> F{Time range policy enabled?}
    F -- No --> G[Maintain FIFO]
    F -- Yes --> H[Apply time range ordering / tie-break]
    G --> I[ReferencePrecalculator consumes ordered indices]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Prepare TDispatchAccessRef]
    J --> K[Dispatcher exposes payload]
    E --> L{Max boundary reached?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Select eviction candidate by oldest time range]
    L -- No --> I
